border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;">北京大学航天中心医院</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">演讲题目：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;">结直肠肿瘤患者正常结肠粘膜的微生物及相关改变</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">祝未非</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span><strong>助理教授</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">美国凯斯西储大学</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">演讲题目：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;">肠道菌磷脂代谢物氧化三甲胺对血小板功能和血栓形成的影响</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">专家们都讲些什么：</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>张发明&nbsp;南京医科大学第二附属医院肠病中心主任</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲题目：</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">粪菌移植体系的研究进展</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲摘要：</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">1.&nbsp;粪菌移植的本质概念</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">2.&nbsp;粪菌移植的临床价值</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">3.&nbsp;粪菌移植的实验室方案和治疗流程</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">4.&nbsp;中华粪菌库-紧急救援计划</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>王则能　克利夫兰诊所项目科学家、凯斯西储大学助理教授</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲题目：</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">肠道细菌代谢产物---氧化三甲胺：从代谢组学到转化医学</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲摘要：</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">我们的研究用基于高效液相-质谱的代谢组学的方法发现了卵磷脂</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">的代谢产物-胆碱、氧化三甲胺、甜菜碱与心血管疾病相关，能早期预测心血管疾病的发生，其中氧化三甲胺的生成依赖于肠道细菌。肠道细菌参与卵磷脂的代谢加快动脉粥样硬化。肠道细菌通过对卵磷脂中的胆碱部分在碳氮键位置切割产生三甲胺，三甲胺为一种气体能在体内扩散，在肝脏中经黄素单加氧酶催化生成氧化三甲胺，氧化三甲胺介导动脉粥样硬化。在载脂蛋白E缺失的小鼠饲料中加入胆碱或氧化三甲胺，能促进小鼠动脉粥样硬化，若用广谱抗生素除去体内的肠道细菌，胆碱对小鼠动脉粥样硬化的促进效应受到逆转。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">另一种含三甲胺的营养物左旋肉碱，富含在红肉中同样通过肠道细菌的切割产生三甲胺进一步氧化为氧化三甲胺而促进小鼠动脉粥样硬化。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">三甲胺类营养物在饮食中普遍存在，所有三甲胺类营养物都有可能通过肠道细菌的切割生成三甲胺进而氧化成氧化三甲胺而导致动脉粥样硬化。因此如何阻止肠道细菌对三甲胺类营养</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">物的切割将成为一个有效地减轻动脉粥样硬化的治疗方案。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">肠道细菌通过三甲胺裂解酶催化含三甲胺官能团化合物在碳氮键位置裂解。我们首先比较胆碱化学结构类似物对胆碱三甲胺裂解酶的抑制效应，而选择了3，3-二甲基-1-丁醇（DMB）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">。DMB对纯化的胆碱三甲胺裂解酶、含此酶的细菌裂解液、完整细菌均表现为抑制效应，DMB能降低食用添加有胆碱饲料的小鼠血中的氧化三甲胺浓度，从而降低胆碱对载脂蛋白E缺失老鼠动脉粥样硬化的促进效应。DMB对多种含三甲胺官能团的化合物被三甲胺裂解酶的裂解显示抑制效应，</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">因此DMB为一种广谱三甲胺类抑制剂，通过抑制多种三甲胺类营养物在肠道中经细菌的切割，降低血中氧化三甲胺的浓度，从而降低动脉粥样硬化。DMB还能改变肠道中细菌的组成，通过降低具有三甲胺裂解酶活性的细菌组成而成为降低血中氧化三甲胺的浓度、治疗动脉粥样硬化的又一途径。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>陈卫　　江南大学食品学院院长</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲题目：</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中国健康人群肠道微生物调查与特征分析</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong>演讲摘要：</strong></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">采集来自我国蒙、汉、藏、维吾尔族等多个民族的健康年轻人群共计314份粪便样品，通过454焦磷酸技术和多元统计方法对其肠道菌群进行分析。在门水平上，中国健康人群肠道</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">中细菌主要隶属于Firmicutes、Bacteroidetes、Proteobacteria和Actinobacteria四个门，在属的水平上，Phascolarctobacterium是中国健康人群肠道中含量最多且个体之间差异最大的微生物。通过基于Unifrac非加权算法的主坐标分析和典范对应分析发现，民族/地域以及城乡生活方式的差异均对中国健康年轻人群的肠道菌群总体结构具有显著影响，其中民族/地域对菌群结构的影响最大，蒙古族和藏族居民的菌群结构尤为独特。而城乡生活方式对菌群结构的影响相对较小，体</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">现出一定的民族/地域特异性。此外研究发现，上述现象不仅与各民族人群的基因型、饮食谱等因素密切相关，亦与各地区的社会经济发展有着内在联系。研究进一步发现，Phascolarctobacterium、Roseburia、Blautia、Faecalibacterium、Clostridium、Subdoligranulum、Ruminococcus、Coprococcus和Bacteroides等9个具有产短链脂肪酸能力的细菌属存在于所有的健康年轻人个体中，且其序列数占总序列数的一半以上。这可能预示着上述9个细菌属在维持人体健康方面具有</span><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;">至关重要的作用，是潜在的有益生态系统服务提供者。</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 23px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">会议地址：</span>上海市徐汇区肇嘉浜路500号。</p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">议场馆：</span>上海好望角大饭店（中科院上海学术活动中心） <br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">来源：生物谷</p><p style="max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br /></p></div><div class="rich_media_tool" id="js_toobar3" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 32px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></div>";}i:1;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"737";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:65:"辞旧迎新岁，羊走猴年到----2016新年晚宴圆满结束";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:2:"54";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1454465309";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1455680345";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"565";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:2881:"<p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">年年岁岁花相似，岁岁年年人不同。我们就这么悄然无息的送走了2015，迎来了2016。在过去的这一年里，锐翌成长了许多，壮大了许多。为了更好的总结这一年里的工作，也为了迎接更美好的2016，锐翌基因在昨晚举办了2016新年晚宴。现场气氛可是相当火热啊~</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201602/03/big_905.jpg" border="0" width="500" height="334" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">2015年锐翌优秀员工<br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201602/03/big_906.jpg" border="0" width="500" height="334" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">各种丰厚大奖<br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201602/03/big_907.jpg" border="0" width="500" height="334" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">超人气游戏——你比划我来猜<br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201602/17/big_922.jpg" border="0" width="540" height="360" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">抽到大奖的同志们笑得很开心</span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一顿新年晚宴，是为2015画上圆满的句号，也是对2016新展望的开始。新年新气象，锐翌会更棒喔~</span><br /></div>";}i:2;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"722";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:60:"锐翌基因应邀参与全国环境微生物学术研讨会";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:3:"120";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1448349300";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1449732283";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"564";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:3453:"<section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI" style="box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 22px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, 宋体;"><span style="color:#333333;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span>&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13px;">由中国微生物学会环境微生物学专业委员会主办，南京农业大学、中国科学院南京土壤研究所、中国科学院南京地理与湖泊研究所、江苏大学环境与安全工程学院承办的“第十八次全国环境微生物学学术研讨会”于2015年11月21日-24日在江苏镇江召开。全国众多从事环境微生物学研究、教学和开发的专家、学者在镇江相聚。本次会议为与会代表提供了一个学术交流、成果展示以及项目合作的良好平台。大会还邀请了院士、国内外环境微生物学领域著名专家、学者报告当今环境微生物学研究的最新成果与发展趋势。</span></section><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">大会也吸引了环境微生物相关企业参会并展示技术和产品。锐翌基因作为对业界十分关注的优秀企业，派出了多名专业人员参与会议，并向各位参会专家展示了我们的技术和产品。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201512/10/big_836.jpg" border="0" width="512" height="382" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><span style="line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;"><br /></span></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><span style="line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;我们还为各位专家学者准备了众多的小礼物。大家都表示非常喜欢,夸赞我们十分有心。</span><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201512/10/big_837.jpg" border="0" width="480" height="641" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><span style="line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;">我们的参会小分队在现场与各位老师专家进行了良好的交流沟通，介绍了我们的产品和相关服务。多位老师表示十分感兴趣，期待与我们的合作。</span><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;"><img src="upfiles/201512/10/big_838.jpg" border="0" width="480" height="641" alt="" /></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><span style="line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family:Microsoft YaHei;font-size:13px;">每一次会议对我们来说都是一次学习的机会，也是和各位老师交流沟通的好时机。以后的会议，我们也会积极参加。希望能够在下次的会议现场和你们进行更</span></span><span style="line-height: 28px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-size: 13px;">好的交流。</span></span><br /></div>";}i:3;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"708";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:75:"锐翌基因应邀参加第十八次全国动物遗传育种学术讨论会";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:3:"239";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1447811694";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1447812407";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"563";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:1775:"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size:13px;">第十八次全国动物遗传育种学术讨论会于2015年11月13-16日在江西南昌顺利召开。大会由中国畜牧兽医学会动物遗传育种学分会主办，江西农业大学动物科技学院承办。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本次会议是国内动物遗传育种领域的一次学术盛会，汇集了上千名国内外从事动物遗传育种教学、科研和生产的专家、学者及技术人员，展示了当今国内外本领域最前沿的研究进展和成果。吴常信、杨焕明、黄路生等院士都参加了会议并进行了主题报告。</span></p><p><br /></p><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/18/big_799.jpg" border="0" width="600" height="451" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p></p><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:13px;"> 锐翌基因也也应邀参加此次会议，与参会专家学者们进行了友好的交流。并跟多家科研院所就宏基因组学研究，动植物重测序，集群构建等项目达成了合作意向。不仅如此，我们还在现场解决了众多学生在组学研究、生物信息分析等多方面的疑问。</span></p><br /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/18/big_800.jpg" border="0" width="600" height="451" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;以后锐翌基因也会积极参与此类会议，给大家提供与我们近距离交流的机会，为大家带去更好的服务。</span></p><br /></div>";}i:4;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"691";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:42:"锐翌基因转录组培训班圆满结束";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:3:"240";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1447052463";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1447139968";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"562";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:2135:"<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/10/big_763.jpg" border="0" width="540" height="360" alt="" /></p><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:13px;"> &nbsp;为期五天的转录组培训班到今天就圆满结束了。一周的时间，大家都留下了美好的记忆，带走了珍贵的知识。</span><span style="font-size: 13px;">培训开始之初，我们的讲师向各位学员介绍了转录组学概论和目前的前沿发展。随后的几天培训中，课程涉及了Linux操作系统入门、有参转录组学分析流程、无参转录组学分析流程、sRNA、R语言、lncRNA、转录组学文章写作方法等多个方面的知识与相关软件的实际操作技术。</span></p><p><br /></p><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/10/big_761.jpg" border="0" width="518" height="384" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size: 13px;"> &nbsp; 在课程中，我们的讲师将理论知识与项目设计结合起来选取了研究中的真实案例进行分析与讲解，并且采用了讲师授课与小组讨论相结合的方法来使学员更好地吸收课程中所学的知识，力求做到理论与实践的统一。在上机实践练习中，我们也安排了多位助教，辅助讲师快速解答学员的疑惑。为了使学员们的研究能够进行得更加顺利，导师们还精心挑选了实际研究中常用的上机软件来展开练习，得到了学员们的一致好评。大家纷纷表示十分实用。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;五天的时间转瞬即逝，培训班就这样圆满结束了。学员们都说，这一期培训班让他们受益良多，学习到的知识与软件操作十分实用。甚至有几位学院迟迟不愿离去，还想多呆一阵，继续多学习一些知识。很多学员也表示，今后我公司若还有其他后续的培训班，他们还会继续参加学习！</span><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><br /></div>";}i:5;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"688";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:48:"金秋技术宣讲在全国各地火热进行中";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:4:"2391";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1446789005";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1446790076";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"561";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:2514:"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp;自9月份开学至今的两个多月时间里，我们已经在北京大学、中国农业科学院、中国海洋大学、四川大学、华南农业大学、华西医院感染疾病研究中心等学校和科研院所举办了多场技术宣讲，也算是跑遍了大江南北。</span><span style="font-size:13px;">在各场宣讲中，我们向各位老师同学介绍了高通量测序前沿技术、案例解析以及课题组具体研究材料的最新研究进展等内容。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/06/big_749.png" border="0" width="480" height="360" alt="" /></p><p><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:13px;">除此之外，还设置了对各课题组研究内容有针对性的知识。老师们也针对转录组方案设计、文章案例、WGCNA、LncRNA等进行了热烈讨论</span><br /></p><p><br /></p><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/06/big_750.png" border="0" width="471" height="353" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;我们的同事在宣讲会现场解答了不少老师和学生提出的问题。宣讲结束后还有不少学生在向我们咨询问题，并询问我们公司是否会在这些院校进行校招。</span></p><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div></div><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201511/06/big_751.png" border="0" alt="" width="470" height="263" /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><br /></div><div style="text-align: left;"><p><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;上一阶段的宣讲进行得十分顺利，也得到了很多老师同学的支持。接下来的时间里，我们会更加努力，为大家带来更加专业化的“干货”。希望能帮助老师和同学更加了解高通量测序技术，给他们答疑解惑，使实验更顺利。</span></p><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><br /></div>";}i:6;a:44:{s:2:"id";s:3:"672";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"161";s:5:"title";s:46:"锐翌基因亮相2015年中国微生物年会";s:8:"subtitle";s:0:"";s:5:"style";s:0:"";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"link_url";s:0:"";s:6:"target";s:1:"0";s:6:"author";s:5:"admin";s:11:"author_type";s:5:"admin";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:4:"hits";s:4:"3343";s:9:"good_hits";s:1:"0";s:8:"bad_hits";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_date";s:10:"1445909317";s:11:"modify_date";s:10:"1445910222";s:8:"thumb_id";s:1:"0";s:5:"istop";s:1:"0";s:7:"isvouch";s:1:"1";s:6:"isbest";s:1:"0";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:6:"points";s:1:"0";s:2:"ip";s:14:"183.247.166.83";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:3:"560";s:8:"htmltype";s:6:"cateid";s:7:"tplfile";s:0:"";s:4:"star";s:1:"0";s:5:"price";s:1:"0";s:14:"price_currency";s:0:"";s:6:"weight";s:1:"0";s:3:"qty";s:1:"0";s:6:"is_qty";s:1:"0";s:8:"qty_unit";s:0:"";s:7:"picture";N;s:2:"df";s:0:"";s:3:"fwb";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:1459:"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size:13px;">为期五天的“2015年中国微生物学会学术年会”目前还在湖北省宜昌市如火如荼的进行着。本次会议共有1200余人参会。我们也派出了“锐翌小分队”前去参与整个会议进程。</span></p><p><br /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201510/27/big_728.jpg" border="0" width="540" height="720" alt="" /></p><p style="text-align: left;"></p><p align="center">奋斗在会议现场的“锐翌小分队”</p><p align="center"><br /></p><br /><div style="text-align: center;"><img src="upfiles/201510/27/big_729.jpg" border="0" width="540" height="344" alt="" /></div><div style="text-align: center;"><p align="center"><span style="font-size: 13px;">现场的小伙伴在热心的给大家解答测序方面的问题</span></p><p align="center"><span style="font-size:13px;"><br /></span></p><p align="center" style="text-align: left;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size:13px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 有幸去到现场的小伙伴表示，本次会议中微生物领域的科研交流十分精彩。他们从专家们的研究中学习到了很多，并激发出了许多新的研究思路。我们派到现场的技术人员也给大家解答了高通量测序的问题，尤其在宏基因组方面非常充分的展示了我们的实力。</span></p><p><br /></p><br /></div>";}}}[§[№[※[◆]※]№]§]97b908cc7f2706244c53fd30d50b8908[◆[№[-[※]-]№]◆]1455775417[◆[№[-[※]-]№]◆]a:19:{s:2:"id";s:2:"40";s:5:"title";s:12:"推荐文章";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:7:"vartext";s:0:"";s:10:"identifier";s:4:"tjwz";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:8:"maxcount";s:1:"7";s:6:"intype";s:4:"sign";s:8:"typetext";s:0:"";s:3:"mid";s:1:"7";s:3:"cid";s:2:"88";s:7:"orderby";s:9:"post_desc";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:5:"inpic";s:0:"";s:12:"pic_required";s:1:"0";s:7:"linkurl";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:7:"isvouch";s:8:"datatype";s:4:"list";s:7:"extsign";s:0:"";}[§[№[※[◆]※]№]§]9be8cd7807be62423efdd1c9c6bf4f23[◆[№[-[※]-]№]◆]1455775417[◆[№[-[※]-]№]◆]a:34:{s:2:"id";s:2:"88";s:10:"identifier";s:12:"keyandongtai";s:6:"langid";s:2:"zh";s:9:"cate_name";s:12:"科研动态";s:8:"parentid";s:2:"86";s:9:"module_id";s:1:"7";s:9:"tpl_index";s:0:"";s:8:"tpl_list";s:0:"";s:8:"tpl_file";s:0:"";s:8:"if_index";s:1:"0";s:5:"taxis";s:2:"22";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:9:"if_hidden";s:1:"0";s:8:"seotitle";s:0:"";s:8:"keywords";s:0:"";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"ifspec";s:1:"0";s:4:"jsjj";s:0:""